---
title: Garlic-Herb Beef & Freekeh Salad with Roast Veggies, Yoghurt & Caramelised Onion
description: Beef and veggies can get a little tiresome, but we bet with this new twist everyone at the table will be wanting a second helping. With flavours of garlic coming from the tender beef strips, a cooling yoghurt dolloped on top of an array of veggies and freekeh, it
can be confirmed that beef and veggies are back in the good books!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/garlic-herb-beef-mixed-grain-salad-911bd335.jpg
